artist.blurb:
Illustrator and concept artist working in the game industry. Currently working as a freelancer.
I have had the good fortune to work with clients such as:
- Creature Caster - 2D Artist.
- Concept Artist at Pixelmadstudios. Project Soulborn.
- Legend Story Studios - «Flesh and Blood TCG»;
- Guildhall Studios - Concept artist on characters;
- Wolff Designa - «Guards of Atlantis II: Tabletop Moba»;
- Burning Manuscripts - «Morneburg`s Chronicles: Deus Vult» visual novel game;
- Concept artist on characters for games «for adults». Not announced project;
- Artworks for book's cover;
-------------
I am a mentor of 2D Art.

